  "title": "[Urgent] - Sales Assistants (No experience ok, Immediate)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sales Assistants Wanted!</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>As a Sales Assistant, you'll be the face of our brands, providing top-notch service and putting a smile on our customer's face :)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Your Mission:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handle customer enquiries </li>\n  <li>Answer questions and offer expert advice</li>\n  <li>Meet sales targets and crush your goals</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>We're Looking For:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Friendly and outgoing personality</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills</li>\n  <li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Passion to above and beyond for customer satisfaction</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Perks:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Opportunities for growth and development</li>\n  <li>Fun and dynamic work environment</li>\n  <li>Overseas Trips</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>If you're a motivated and outgoing individual who loves customer engagement, we'd love to hear from you!</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>",
